name: NEW! Featured Product! DicE Magazine X Dan Collins poster
description: In the spirit of the old underground pulp comics of the 60's, this huge 24"x36" poster was designed by Dan Collins of Old Gold Garage for DicE magazine. There were a limited run of 200 posters printed, 175 of which were sold by DicE and are completely sold out. The final 25 posters were signed and numbered by Dan Collins 1-25, and are only available here. These will not last long, so do not wait if you want one. The detail is amazing. These will not be re printed.

name: NEW! Featured product! Cobra King "Snake Charmer" seats for rigid frames
description:
This has been a long time coming but the wait is over! Rigid frame Cobra King seats are here, and they are the best on the market and hand made here in Ventura Ca. As usual the pans are constructed of heavy gauge steel, not fiberglass or plastic. They are available in wide or narrow rear sections, the wide has the passenger section at 5" wide and the narrow has the passenger section at 4" wide. Mounting is up to the builder, there are 3 nuts flush welded into the all steel pan, you can bolt these to the frame or use a hinged mount to access your oil fill. 

These are also available in all leather for a $60 surcharge

*These are NOT designed for use on softails but they may work with some bracket modifications, at your discretion

**these are NOT designed for use on early swingarm frames please see our Cobra King Swingarm seats for that application

name: Old Gold "Daytona" full face helmets
description:
At last, a full face helmet that looks great and is comfortable to wear. These are a collaboration between Dan Collins and TT&Co. from tokyo. Dan Collins designed his version of the "vintage" full face helmet, and the masters at TT&Co. brought his design to life. Featuring brass hardware and D rings, A removable and washable interior liner, and chrome edging. These come in three colors,Oakland Orange, Jet Black, and Ivory White, and 5 different sizes to make sure everyone can find the size for them. They also come with a limited edition helmet bag and box.

name: NEW! Old Gold "Bat Wing" CV carb brackets for Sportster
description:
these are a must have if you're running an aftermarket air cleaner or velocity stack, or taking the time to detail your engine, and recommended to use when you use breather bolts like the ones BCM makes(Willis Bolts: for sale here also). They hold the carb tight in the rubber coupler of the intake manifold and look great while doing it. Hand made in the USA out of lightweight aluminum. These will bolt on in about 5 minutes. Sold as a pair. 
fits '91-'06 Sportster (XL)

name: NEW! "Willis Bolts" breather bolts from BCM
description:
I sell these because I use them on every top end breathing Harley I build. These are a perfect match for our Old Gold Garage "Bat Wing" CV carb brackets! And these are made right here in Southern California...sold as a pair

•Willis Bolts are fully machined from 303 Stainless Steel

•broached to internally use a ¼" hex key and to top it off the we thought a machined stainless washer made in the identical diameter is the cleanest way to go.

•Bolt them up, install the stainless mesh, Uni foam, circlip and your good to go.

•We strongly suggest applying a dot of blue thread lock on all threads during installation.

1/2x13 Thread

Made in USA

name: Old Gold "Cobra King" seat: early swingarm/ bigtwin frames

name: NEW! Old Gold "Bullseye" CV carb tops

**These come with stainless hardware

Fits Big Twins and Sportsters

This product is MADE IN THE USA!

name: Sportster/Buell/Big Twin performance clutch
description: HIGH PERFORMANCE EXTRA PLATE KIT 1990-97 Big-Twin & 1991 to Present Sportster (XL) from Energy One. Includes 9 race proven material friction plates on tempered steel cores. Starburst groove pattern for maximum heat dissipation & oil circulation. Included are 8 tempered steel drive plates. Pre-set stack height for easy installation. 15% more clutch area for high performance strokers. Includes 15% stronger diaphragm spring. Remove OEM rivet plate! 15% MORE SURFACE AREA THAN STOCK. We sell these parts because we use them in our own bikes. Made in Southern California!

name: Buell Blast performance kevlar clutch
description: This kit from Energy One will fit all Buell Blasts, These work great and are usually cheaper than buying from the dealer. Includes 5 race proven material friction plates on tempered steel cores. Starburst groove pattern for maximum heat dissipation and oil circulation. Included are 5 tempered steel drive plates and a 15% stronger than stock diaphragm clutch spring. Clutch has 15% more surface area and a pre-measured stack height for easy, accurate installation. MAKE THAT BLAST DO WHEELIES!

name: NEW! Kevlar lined leather riding gloves
description:
These gloves are constructed of premium grain leather that is treated for water and fade resistance. The wrist length design with elastic cuffs makes for an easy fit for most individuals, and the 100% Kevlar knit liners provides insulation and protection that regular leather gloves can't, while also giving the rider a comfortable fit and "Feel". 

available in small-XX Large

Glove Sizing:
Please use the glove chart to find your approximate glove size. Remember, no two hands are alike. Finger length relative to palm size is not constant from person to person. Additionally, what constitutes a comfortable fit can vary considerably between individuals. Using the chart below will help you to find an approximate glove size, but no method of measurement can substitute for actually trying them on.

***These are made in Pakistan, not the USA. I am currently working on sourcing an American supplier, because our ultimate Goal is to sell 100% American made parts and accessories. Thanks
